name: 1 Verify auto-dispo can be enabled and disabled in Org Settings
fullName: 1 Verify auto-dispo can be enabled and disabled in Org Settings

steps.name: assert expected **.toast** not to exist in the DOM
assert expected **<div.ui-view-main.ng-scope>** to contain text **Org Settings**
assert expected **<toggle#autoDispoToggle.ng-untouched.ng-valid.ng-scope.ng-isolate-scope.ng-not-empty.ng-dirty.ng-valid-parse>** not to have class **off**
assert expected **.toast** not to exist in the DOM
assert expected **<toggle#autoDispoToggle.ng-untouched.ng-valid.ng-scope.ng-isolate-scope.ng-not-empty.ng-dirty.ng-valid-parse>** not to have class **off**
assert expected **.toast** not to exist in the DOM
